# Add New Bible Version

- [ ] Analyze existing Bible data structure <!-- id: 0 -->
    - [ ] Check `src/data` content
    - [ ] Read `BiblePage.jsx` implementation
    - [ ] Understand JSON format of Bible text
- [ ] Obtain new Bible data <!-- id: 1 -->
    - [ ] Ask user for the new Bible data source or file
    - [ ] Format data to match existing structure
- [ ] Implement changes <!-- id: 2 -->
    - [ ] Add new data file to `src/data`
    - [ ] Update `BiblePage.jsx` to include the new version option
- [ ] Verify changes <!-- id: 3 -->
    - [ ] Test if the new version appears and loads correctly
